title: ATES Networks
description:
About ATES Networks

Created in 2008, ATES Networks develops, implements and supports professional solutions for mobile operators, service and content providers. Our solutions are designed to deliver rich content and innovative value added services for all networks: mobile and next-generation networks (2,5G, 3G, 3,5G, 4G), WLAN, WiMax, ... .

Intelligence at the Network Edge

Our leading product suite – BroadApp – is a complete mobile solution which enables our customers to deliver information, personalized content and services to end users, based on intelligent applications for mobile devices.

Patented Technologies

ATES Networks, continuously innovates and creates technologies which enable telecommunication, service and content providers to instantly deliver new services and information to their subscribers, and create a great, new user experience.

Thanks to these technologies, Time to market – required for the design and deployment of new services and applications - is also dramatically reduced.
